&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;q
0 g
0 0 95.5444 -211.7696 480.23346 474.70703 cm
BX
/Sh15 sh
EX
Q
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The 0 0 creates a matrix that has a scale and a shear of 0. That can&apos;t be good. I&apos;m now using a default in case of error and the file renders (although not as good as Adobe). The error you posted is non fatal, it is the NPE coming after that was fatal. The error will still be posted, now with an extra detail.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
